If you have any problems, please contact us at info@samtechnologies.ca

SAM Premier offers the most comprehensive voice controlled smart home experience with Alexa. Control your lights and other devices hands free. Just say it, SAM Premier will obey. 

Here’s a step by step instructions:
(1). Download our " SAM Premier" app in Google Play or IOS App Store;
(2). Launch the app and sign up a new account (or sign in if you’re already registered);
(3). Turn on SAM Premier devices and connect them with “SAM Premier” app;
(4). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Amazon Market, Google Play or IOS App Store, and connect Echo dot with "Alexa" app;
(5). Search the Alexa skills directory for " SAM Premier ";
(6). Click Enable skill of "SAM Premier", then input your account username, password and region on the linking page;
(7). Talk to Echo dot “Alexa, discover devices”. Wait till Echo dot says "Discover is completed";
(8). Now all setup is done. Try talk to Echo dot to control your devices.

Here are part of the voice commands SAM Premier have:

Plugs:
* Alexa, turn on light
* Alexa, turn off light
